(1230, '3257061269', 'Der Alchimist.', 'Paulo Coelho', '2003', 'Diogenes Verlag, ZÃ?Â¼rich', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/3257061269.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'He fought his first battle on the Scottish Highlands in 1536. He will fight his greatest battle on the streets of New York City in 1986. His name is Connor MacLeod. He is immortal.', 5, '2022-01-05', 0, 'der-alchimist', 842),
(1231, '3453210999', 'Das Lied der alten Steine.', 'Barbara Erskine', '2002', 'Heyne', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/3453210999.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'When petty criminal Luke Jackson is sentenced to two years in a Florida prison farm, he doesn\'t play by the rules of either the sadistic warden or the yard\'s resident heavy, Dragline, who ends up admiring the new guy\'s unbreakable will. Luke\'s bravado, even in the face of repeated stints in the prison\'s dreaded solitary confinement cell, \"the box,\" make him a rebel hero to his fellow convicts and a thorn in the side of the prison officers.', 2, '2022-01-05', 0, 'das-lied-der-alten-steine', 1286),
